{"tid":1834002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國確診第4宗新型冠狀病毒病例　屬首名泰國人感染","createTime":"2020-01-22T07:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:59:59.000Z","uid":51620,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5696fba6e69ef05a69aedb325d4bb284e803f401","tid":1834002,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"泰國傳媒報道，當地確診第4宗新型冠狀病毒感染病例，患者為泰國女性，是首名確診的泰國人，她去年底曾到過武漢。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述泰國公共衛生部消息，表示患者73歲，去年底曾到訪武漢，目前在佛統市一間醫院接受治療，病情正在好轉。她早前返抵泰國時，因為發燒被隔離，其後確診。<br />\n<br />\n泰國境內已出現的4宗確診病例，3人是中國籍，其中2人已經康復返國，第3人正在當地接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n泰國公共衛生部表示，目前當地疫情可控，並已採取措施防止疫情擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504177-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504177-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=04431659\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504177-20200122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=743126c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504177-20200122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f421afe8dd945953bdfb71ac8a30ed3da2d06bd2","tid":1834002,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"成廿鳩幾日潛伏期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d350d67ef392c30f1635996c2a917d2f82cc5991","tid":1834002,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"成個月前都奶嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c21c29992373a78fd50b0591d7f04ce9914934a","tid":1834002,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"Join the club!!!"},{"pid":"9d7376e71b47aaf1d68f9caa58d5b31cd7947378","tid":1834002,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1